item.title: Comment on Why You Should Use AE Templates? by Paul
item.dc:creator: Paul
item.description: I wonder if there’s any reason why the same can’t be said for simply staying up later? If it’s about time to do nothing, or to exercise, or to be bored, you would assume the same can be achieved at 1am when you haven’t slept yet as it can at 5am when you’ve just gotten up.
item.content:encoded: I wonder if there’s any reason why the same can’t be said for simply staying up later? If it’s about time to do nothing, or to exercise, or to be bored, you would assume the same can be achieved at 1am when you haven’t slept yet as it can at 5am when you’ve just gotten up.
